description: Look your best with the Alexander McQueen oversized sneaker. Crafted from premium white smooth calf leather, this lace-up sneaker features a sophisticated black suede heel detailing and large flat laces for maximum comfort. For added convenience, a second set of laces is included – so you can express your individuality to its fullest. As part of our commitment to reducing our carbon footprint and minimizing cotton consumption, we no longer offer a dust bag for our sneakers; however, we are sure you’ll agree that the chic style and enduring comfort of this Alexander McQueen shoe speaks volumes without it.
